    "/ExternalDoxiAPI/SetSignatures": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Obsolete"
        ],
        "description": "SetSignatures - Fill a flow fields for one user\n## JSON object description:\n\n* * *\n## exSetSignFlowRequest:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * SignerKey | ***ParticipantKey*** | The Signer that need to do the action |\n| DeclineComments | String(4000) | Only requerd in Decline action (signAction=1) |\n| SignAction | ***SignAction*** | The action that need to do |\n| SignImageBase64 | String | Base-64 image of the signature - Only in Sign action (signAction=0) |\n| BrowserDetails | String | Base-64 of the JSON of the browsers that signed (for record on the signature metadata) - Only in Sign action (signAction=0) |\n| IPAddress | String | IP address of the signer that sign the document  |\n| FlowElements | ***FlowElementData[]*** | Elements that need to fill with signer value - Only in Sign action (signAction=0/2) |\n| AttachedFiles | String[] | File IDs (Use method ex/flow/:signFlowId/attachments) |\n\n* * *\n### FlowElementData:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * ElementId | String Validation: Invalid GUID format | Element ID |\n| TextData | String(4000) | Value of the field |\n\n* * *\n### SignAction:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | Approve |\n| 1 | Decline |\n| 2 | Save |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKey:\n\n### Allow to locate Doxi user by:UserEmail=1UserPhone=2\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Key | String | User search value |\n| Type | ***ParticipantKeyType*** | Search type:UserEmail=1,UserPhone=2 |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKeyType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | UserId |\n| 1 | UserEmail |\n| 2 | UserPhone |\n| 3 | UserName |\n| 4 | GroupId |\n",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "X-Tenant",
            "in": "header",
            "description": "Tenant Name",
