    "/ExternalDoxiAPI/GetFlowsByFilter": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Obsolete"
        ],
        "description": "Get flows by filter parameters\n## JSON object description:\n\n* * *\n## getFlowsByFilterRequest:\n\n### CustomFields: Key value; SignatureFlowStatus:Open=0,Approved=1, Declined=2,Stopped=3,Suspended=4\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| CustomFields | KeyValuePair\\<String,String\\>[] | Search flows be CustomFields property Key+Value |\n| SignatureFlowStatus | ***Nullable\\<SignatureFlowStatus\\>*** | Search flow by Flow status |\n| Signer | ***ParticipantKey*** | Searche by the flow signer |\n| Sender | ***ParticipantKey*** | Search by the user that create the flow (sender) |\n| FromDate | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Search by flow create date - from |\n| ToDate | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Search by flow create date - to |\n| Description | String | Search by flow description name |\n| KitId | String | Search by kit Id |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKey:\n\n### Allow to locate Doxi user by:UserEmail=1UserPhone=2\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Key | String | User search value |\n| Type | ***ParticipantKeyType*** | Search type:UserEmail=1,UserPhone=2 |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKeyType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | UserId |\n| 1 | UserEmail |\n| 2 | UserPhone |\n| 3 | UserName |\n| 4 | GroupId |\n\n* * *\n### SignatureFlowStatus:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | Open |\n| 1 | Approved |\n| 2 | Declined |\n| 3 | Stopped |\n| 4 | Suspended |\n| 5 | Expired |\n",
        "parameters": [
          {
