    "/ex/template/CreateFlowFromTemplate/{templateId}": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Obsolete"
        ],
        "description": " Create new flow from template\n\n* * *\n## templateId:\n\n\n* * *\n## createFlowFromTemplateRequest:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Description | String | The description/name of the flow |\n| * SenderKey | ***ParticipantKey*** | Id of the Sender |\n| CustomFields | KeyValuePair\\<String,String\\>[] | Add additional data in the flow |\n| Users | ***ExUser[]*** | The changable users of the flow |\n| PermanentSignersSettings | ***ExPermanentSignerSettings[]*** | Additional settings for permanent signers |\n| Recipients | ***ExUser[]*** | All the CC users of the flow |\n| IsNoSend | Boolean | Disable/Enable receive emails of the flow |\n| ReadOnlyFields | ***ReadOnlyField[]*** | Elements with readonly value (the signer can't change the value) |\n| PackageId | String |  Id of the package (the flow will be assigned to package) |\n| PackageName | String | Name of the package |\n| SenderNotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of emails notification (for the sender and CC),Allowed values: 0,1,3,4,5,7,9,12,13,14,15 |\n| IsAutomaticRemainder | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Enable/Disable send automatic remainder |\n| DayesForAutomaticRemainder | Nullable\\<Int32\\> | Number of the days for getting automatic remainder |\n| IsSendApprovalMailToAllSigners | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Enabled/Diabaled send email to all signers (when the flow approved) |\n| PreliminaryText | String | Preliminary text of the flow (display only in side by side mode)  |\n| SignFlowDescriptionMessage | String |  Description of the document in the email |\n| DisableSBS | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Enable dispaly side by side mode in the flow |\n| FlowTwoFactorEnabled | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Enable/Disable Two Factor on the flow |\n| SignersIndexToRemove | Int32[] | The index of the signer to remove from the flow (The first index is one) |\n| FlowExpirationDate | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Expiration date of the flow |\n| KitId | String |  |\n\n* * *\n### ReadOnlyField:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * ElementLabel | String | Label of element |\n| Value | String | Value of element |\n| TextSize | Int32 | Size ot element text  |\n| TextFont | String | Font of element text |\n\n* * *\n### ExPermanentSignerSettings:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * SignerIndex | Int32 | The index of the signer in the template, starting from 0. |\n| EnableAdditionalMessageDelivery | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Indicates whether the signing link should be sent via additional messaging channels(e.g., SMS or WhatsApp) in addition to email. |\n| IsDisableAttachment | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Enable add attachments to the flow |\n| IsSuspended | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Set status flow to suspended when the signer need to sign |\n| IsNoDecline | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Endable Decline option in flow  |\n| NotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of email notifications |\n| MinimumSignatures | Nullable\\<Int32\\> | When the user have optional signature element - Dox validate the minimum signatures in the document |\n| ForceApprovalOnSignature | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Force approval on signature |\n| PersonalMessage | String(300) Validation: The field cannot contain script, vbscript, or style tags. | Personal message to the signer |\n| UserPasswordDescription | ***LanguageKey[]*** | Display when the user open the linkfor example: \"Please enter your social security number\"LanguageKey is the message with all supported languages |\n\n* * *\n### ExUser:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * UserKey | ***ParticipantKey*** | Id of user |\n| Email | String(77) | Email of user  |\n| FirstName | String(50) | First name of user |\n| LastName | String(50) | Last name of user |\n| SmsPhoneNumber | String(80) | Phone Number of user (if empty, the user will not receive sms) |\n| UserPassword | String Validation: Only letters, numbers, and special characters are allowed. | Password for opening the sign link  |\n| Company | String(80) | Company name of user |\n| Title | String(80) | Title of user |\n| IsDisableAttachment | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Enable add attachments to the flow |\n| IsSuspended | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Set status flow to suspended when the signer need to sign |\n| IsNoDecline | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Endable Decline option in flow  |\n| NotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of email notifications |\n| MinimumSignatures | Nullable\\<Int32\\> | When the user have optional signature element - Dox validate the minimum signatures in the document |\n| ForceApprovalOnSignature | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Force approval on signature |\n| PersonalMessage | String(300) Validation: The field cannot contain script, vbscript, or style tags. | Personal message to the signer |\n| UserPasswordDescription | ***LanguageKey[]*** | Display when the user open the linkfor example: \"Please enter your social security number\"LanguageKey is the message with all supported languages |\n\n* * *\n### LanguageKey:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| Language | String | language : 'en-US','he-IL' |\n| Value | String | Value of text |\n\n* * *\n### NotificationMails[]:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | All |\n| 1 | None |\n| 2 | SignFlow |\n| 3 | FlowApproved |\n| 4 | FlowDeclined |\n| 5 | FlowStart |\n| 6 | ReminderToSignFlow |\n| 7 | FlowStoppedToSender |\n| 8 | FlowStoppedToSigner |\n| 9 | KitCompleted |\n| 10 | SignKit |\n| 11 | ReminderToSignKit |\n| 12 | KitCreated |\n| 13 | FlowExpired |\n| 14 | FlowCCApproved |\n| 15 | FlowCCDeclined |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKey:\n\n### Allow to locate Doxi user by:UserEmail=1UserPhone=2\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Key | String | User search value |\n| Type | ***ParticipantKeyType*** | Search type:UserEmail=1,UserPhone=2 |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKeyType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | UserId |\n| 1 | UserEmail |\n| 2 | UserPhone |\n| 3 | UserName |\n| 4 | GroupId |\n",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "templateId",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "X-Tenant",
            "in": "header",
            "description": "Tenant Name",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "default": "{{Tenant}}"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json-patch+json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/CreateFlowFromTemplateRequest"
              },
              "example": {
                "TemplateId": "d583e9e1-3633-420a-aa45-793b4653bac1",
                "Description": "Create flow from template example",
                "SenderKey": {
                  "Key": "doxiUser",
                  "Type": 3
                },
                "CustomFields": [
                  {
                    "Key": "SomeInnerSystemIdNumber",
                    "Value": "12345"
                  }
                ],
