        "description": "\n\n* * *\n## subscriptionId:\n\n\n* * *\n## requestWebhook:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| FromDateTime | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Search by WebhookSenderLog create date - fromFormat: dd/mm/yyyy |\n| ToDateTime | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Search by WebhookSenderLog create date - toFormat: dd/mm/yyyy |\n| IsFailed | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | The filter parameter for the success status of records: true for failed, false for successful, null for all. |\n",
