    "/v6/flows/{signFlowId}/action": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Flow"
        ],
        "description": "[V6] Change flow status by performing an action\n\n* * *\n## signFlowId:\n\n### The unique identifier (GUID) of the flow\n\n* * *\n## setFlowActionRequest:\n\n### Request containing the action to perform. FlowAction values: StopFlow=0, ResendDeclinedFlow=1, SendReminder=2, ArchiveFlow=3\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * FlowAction | ***FlowExternalAction*** | FlowAction: StopFlow=0 ResendDeclinedFlow=1 SendReminder=2 ArchiveFlow=3 |\n| SenderKey | ***ParticipantKey*** |  Required for actions:  1. ResendDeclinedFlow - flow creator or admin user 2. ArchiveFlow - a participant in the flow (creator or signer) Not required for actions:  1. StopFlow 2. SendReminder |\n| IsRecover | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> |  Required for action: ArchiveFlow To archive a flow - IsRecover = false To remove a flow from archive - IsRecover = true |\n| SignerKey | ***ParticipantKey*** |  Optional for actions:  1. SendReminder - the signer who should receive the reminder (only in a parallel process) 2. ResendDeclinedFlow - Restore a flow for specific signer, sign staus will be changed from decline to waiting for approval Not required for actions:  1. StopFlow 2. ArchiveFlow |\n| SignerIndex | Nullable\\<Int32\\> | The order of the signer in a flow  Required for ResendDeclinedFlow action in case of multiple signers in parallel flow  |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKey:\n\n### Allow to locate Doxi user by:UserEmail=1UserPhone=2\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Key | String | User search value |\n| Type | ***ParticipantKeyType*** | Search type:UserEmail=1,UserPhone=2 |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKeyType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | UserId |\n| 1 | UserEmail |\n| 2 | UserPhone |\n| 3 | UserName |\n| 4 | GroupId |\n\n* * *\n### FlowExternalAction:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | StopFlow |\n| 1 | ResendDeclinedFlow |\n| 2 | SendReminder |\n| 3 | ArchiveFlow |\n| 4 | ReleaseFlow |\n",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "signFlowId",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "X-Tenant",
            "in": "header",
            "description": "Tenant Name",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "default": "{{Tenant}}"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json-patch+json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SetFlowActionRequest"
              },
              "example": {
                "FlowAction": 0,
                "SenderKey": {
                  "Key": "sender@example.com",
                  "Type": 1
                },
                "UserKey": {
                  "Key": "sender@example.com",
                  "Type": 1
                },
                "IsRecover": false,
                "SignerKey": {
                  "Key": "signer@example.com",
                  "Type": 1
                },
                "SignerIndex": 0
              }
            },
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
