    "/v6/kits/single/{kitId}": {
      "put": {
        "tags": [
          "Kits"
        ],
        "description": "[V6] Update existing kit with new configuration\n\n* * *\n## kitId:\n\n### The unique identifier (GUID) of the kit to update\n\n* * *\n## exUpdateKitRequest:\n\n### Request containing updated kit configuration including kit name, description, documents (optional), and participant information. Only provided fields will be updated.\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Signer | ***ExUser*** | Signer who is required to sign the flows included in the kit |\n| Templates | ***ExKitTemplate[]*** | Templates assigned to the kit |\n| Flows | ***ExKitFlow[]*** | Flows assigned to the kit |\n| * KitAction | ***SingleKitAction*** | The action to do after creating the kit - only save in DB or send the kit to the signer. |\n| SendingMethods | ***SendMethodTypes[]*** | Options to send the sign request to the signer (in case of null, the signer won't receive a request to sign) |\n| IsUseCompanyNameInMessage | Boolean | Sending the request to sign by name of the company instead of the sender name |\n| SignFlowDescriptionMessage | String | Additional information in the request to sign message |\n| SignerNotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of emails notification for the sender and CC,Allowed values: 0,1,3,4,5,7,9,12,13,14,15 |\n| SenderNotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of emails notification for the signer,Allowed values: 0,1,2,6,8,10,11 |\n| * IsTwoFactorEnabled | Boolean | Two-factor authentication for the signer. |\n| * KitDescription | String(100) | The display name of the kit. |\n| * SenderKey | ***ParticipantKey*** | Id of the Sender |\n| PreliminaryText | String(1000) | Optional introductory text displayed to the kit signer in the lobby screen. |\n| ExternalLinks | ***ExExternalLink[]*** | Optional collection of related external links (for integrations or metadata). |\n| Recipients | ***ExUser[]*** | Optional list of CC recipients associated with the kit. |\n\n* * *\n### ExExternalLink:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| Description | String(100) |  |\n| Url | String |  |\n\n* * *\n### SendMethodTypes[]:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | SMS |\n| 1 | EMail |\n\n* * *\n### SingleKitAction:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | Save |\n| 1 | Send |\n\n* * *\n### ExKitFlow:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * SignFlowId | String |  |\n| * Order | Int32 | Defines the display order of flows in the kit signing lobby. |\n\n* * *\n### ExKitTemplate:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Order | Int32 | Defines the display order of flows from template in the kit signing lobby. |\n| * TemplateId | String |  |\n| DynamicSigners | ***ExUser[]*** | Dynamic signers in template, to enable notification fill SmsPhoneNumber property. |\n| PermanentSignerSettings | ***ExPermanentSignerSettings[]*** | Permanent signers additional settings. |\n\n* * *\n### ExPermanentSignerSettings:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * SignerIndex | Int32 | The index of the signer in the template, starting from 0. |\n| EnableAdditionalMessageDelivery | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Indicates whether the signing link should be sent via additional messaging channels(e.g., SMS or WhatsApp) in addition to email. |\n| IsDisableAttachment | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Enable add attachments to the flow |\n| IsSuspended | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Set status flow to suspended when the signer need to sign |\n| IsNoDecline | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Endable Decline option in flow  |\n| NotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of email notifications |\n| MinimumSignatures | Nullable\\<Int32\\> | When the user have optional signature element - Dox validate the minimum signatures in the document |\n| ForceApprovalOnSignature | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Force approval on signature |\n| PersonalMessage | String(300) Validation: The field cannot contain script, vbscript, or style tags. | Personal message to the signer |\n| UserPasswordDescription | ***LanguageKey[]*** | Display when the user open the linkfor example: \"Please enter your social security number\"LanguageKey is the message with all supported languages |\n\n* * *\n### ExUser:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * UserKey | ***ParticipantKey*** | Id of user |\n| Email | String(77) | Email of user  |\n| FirstName | String(50) | First name of user |\n| LastName | String(50) | Last name of user |\n| SmsPhoneNumber | String(80) | Phone Number of user (if empty, the user will not receive sms) |\n| UserPassword | String Validation: Only letters, numbers, and special characters are allowed. | Password for opening the sign link  |\n| Company | String(80) | Company name of user |\n| Title | String(80) | Title of user |\n| IsDisableAttachment | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Enable add attachments to the flow |\n| IsSuspended | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Set status flow to suspended when the signer need to sign |\n| IsNoDecline | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Disable/Endable Decline option in flow  |\n| NotificationMailsToSend | ***NotificationMails[]*** | Types of email notifications |\n| MinimumSignatures | Nullable\\<Int32\\> | When the user have optional signature element - Dox validate the minimum signatures in the document |\n| ForceApprovalOnSignature | Nullable\\<Boolean\\> | Force approval on signature |\n| PersonalMessage | String(300) Validation: The field cannot contain script, vbscript, or style tags. | Personal message to the signer |\n| UserPasswordDescription | ***LanguageKey[]*** | Display when the user open the linkfor example: \"Please enter your social security number\"LanguageKey is the message with all supported languages |\n\n* * *\n### LanguageKey:\n\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| Language | String | language : 'en-US','he-IL' |\n| Value | String | Value of text |\n\n* * *\n### NotificationMails[]:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | All |\n| 1 | None |\n| 2 | SignFlow |\n| 3 | FlowApproved |\n| 4 | FlowDeclined |\n| 5 | FlowStart |\n| 6 | ReminderToSignFlow |\n| 7 | FlowStoppedToSender |\n| 8 | FlowStoppedToSigner |\n| 9 | KitCompleted |\n| 10 | SignKit |\n| 11 | ReminderToSignKit |\n| 12 | KitCreated |\n| 13 | FlowExpired |\n| 14 | FlowCCApproved |\n| 15 | FlowCCDeclined |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKey:\n\n### Allow to locate Doxi user by:UserEmail=1UserPhone=2\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Key | String | User search value |\n| Type | ***ParticipantKeyType*** | Search type:UserEmail=1,UserPhone=2 |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKeyType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | UserId |\n| 1 | UserEmail |\n| 2 | UserPhone |\n| 3 | UserName |\n| 4 | GroupId |\n",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "kitId",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "X-Tenant",
            "in": "header",
            "description": "Tenant Name",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "default": "{{Tenant}}"
            }
          }
        ],
