    "/v6/kits/single/search": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Kits"
        ],
        "description": "Search kit by parameters\n## JSON object description:\n\n* * *\n## searchKitRequest:\n\n### The search parameter\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| ConstantKitId | String Validation: Invalid GUID format | Filter by Constant kit id |\n| SignFlowId | String Validation: Invalid GUID format | Filter by flow id exists in the kit |\n| FromCreateDate | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Filter by start creation date |\n| ToCreateDate | Nullable\\<DateTime\\> | Filter by end creation date |\n| Status | ***Nullable\\<KitStatusType\\>*** | Filter by Kit status |\n| MainSigner | ***ParticipantKey*** | Filter by main signer participant key |\n| CreatedBy | ***ParticipantKey*** | Filter by creator participant key |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKey:\n\n### Allow to locate Doxi user by:UserEmail=1UserPhone=2\n| ***filed*** | ***type*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ | ------ |\n| * Key | String | User search value |\n| Type | ***ParticipantKeyType*** | Search type:UserEmail=1,UserPhone=2 |\n\n* * *\n### ParticipantKeyType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | UserId |\n| 1 | UserEmail |\n| 2 | UserPhone |\n| 3 | UserName |\n| 4 | GroupId |\n\n* * *\n### KitStatusType:\n\n| ***value*** | ***description*** |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0 | Open |\n| 1 | Completed |\n| 2 | NotSend |\n| 3 | Deleted |\n| 4 | InProgress |\n",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "X-Tenant",
            "in": "header",
            "description": "Tenant Name",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "default": "{{Tenant}}"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json-patch+json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SearchKitRequest"
              },
              "example": {
                "ConstantKitId": "2ffa889a-c257-4128-a1d5-51b7ec77644c",
                "SignFlowId": "aA14ff66-dC54-441F-d5EE-82fe69bFEd5E",
                "FromCreateDate": "07/05/2002 19:41:01",
                "ToCreateDate": "09/04/1952 06:33:24",
                "Status": 3,
                "MainSigner": {
                  "Key": "0521234567",
                  "Type": 2
                },
                "CreatedBy": {
                  "Key": "someUser@someCompany.com",
                  "Type": 1
                }
              }
            },
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SearchKitRequest"
              },
              "example": {
                "ConstantKitId": "2ffa889a-c257-4128-a1d5-51b7ec77644c",
                "SignFlowId": "aA14ff66-dC54-441F-d5EE-82fe69bFEd5E",
                "FromCreateDate": "07/05/2002 19:41:01",
                "ToCreateDate": "09/04/1952 06:33:24",
                "Status": 3,
                "MainSigner": {
                  "Key": "0521234567",
                  "Type": 2
                },
                "CreatedBy": {
                  "Key": "someUser@someCompany.com",
                  "Type": 1
                }
              }
            },
            "text/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SearchKitRequest"
              },
              "example": {
                "ConstantKitId": "2ffa889a-c257-4128-a1d5-51b7ec77644c",
                "SignFlowId": "aA14ff66-dC54-441F-d5EE-82fe69bFEd5E",
                "FromCreateDate": "07/05/2002 19:41:01",
                "ToCreateDate": "09/04/1952 06:33:24",
                "Status": 3,
                "MainSigner": {
                  "Key": "0521234567",
                  "Type": 2
                },
                "CreatedBy": {
                  "Key": "someUser@someCompany.com",
                  "Type": 1
                }
              }
            },
            "application/*+json": {
              "schema": {
